OL,2,MWhat does a quantum computer actually
OL,4,Mdo?
OL,6,CMatt Wallace
OL,7,CFri 19:40-20:10
OL,8,CStage A
OL,10,GInside a trapped-ion quantum computer,
OL,11,Gwhat really happens when you run a
OL,12,Gprogram? This talk follows a single
OL,13,Gcalculation end-to-end. From ions
OL,14,Gbeing loaded and cooled in a trap,
OL,15,Gthrough a sequence of laser pulses
OL,16,Gthat implement quantum gates, to the
OL,17,Gfinal measurement that produces a
OL,18,Gresult. Along the way, we’ll unpack
OL,19,Ghow qubits are physically realised in
OL,20,Gatomic states, and how carefully
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
